  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/9bd94812cf06cf618e030c3291d9dad4.avif?t=1744034116\" width=650 height=1237 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHO WILL BECOME THE ULTIMATE CHECKOUT CHAMPION?</h2>In Checkout! you compete to be the first player to turn in all the items in your shopping list. We have a variety of  environments, game modes, and modifiers for you to enjoy. Up to 4 players can play locally or online via Steam Remote Play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/5d462785491ab23ec7db9de907284bff.poster.avif?t=1744034116\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/5d462785491ab23ec7db9de907284bff.webm?t=1744034116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/5d462785491ab23ec7db9de907284bff.mp4?t=1744034116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIDIMENSIONAL MARKET MAYHEM</h2>Prove your worth in supermarkets from different dimensions, each with its own set of unique items, hazards and traps.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/4fac97537ed4609bc534e26a18019e81.poster.avif?t=1744034116\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/4fac97537ed4609bc534e26a18019e81.webm?t=1744034116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/4fac97537ed4609bc534e26a18019e81.mp4?t=1744034116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEMODE GALORE</h2>Your skills will be put to the test in a variaty of game modes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757500/extras/5f1a992eaffab2271eba9a4cf6d59755.avif?t=1744034116\" width=601 height=139 /></span>",
